  "notes": "Captured Admin GraphQL 2026-04 URL scheme validation for external marketing activities. Shopify accepts http/https, rejects ftp/file/mailto at the mutation field validator as top-level INVALID_FIELD_ARGUMENTS with data.<root> null, and rejects data:/javascript: through URL scalar coercion as INVALID_VARIABLE before resolver handling. The upsert root enforces the same rule in the captured public Admin API. Read-back targets prove rejected create/update inputs do not stage or mutate marketing activity state."
